Package org.openbel.framework.core.df.beldata.equivalence

Captures the equivalence file's header model (.beleq file).

See:
          Description

Class Summary
EquivalenceBlock EquivalenceBlock encapsulates the '[Equivalence]' block of a BEL equivalence document.
EquivalenceHeader EquivalenceHeader represents a BEL equivalence file's header section including the four, required blocks: Equivalence block - Describes the equivalence document and what type of data is defined Author block - Describes the author of this equivalence document Citation block - Describes the citation of this equivalence document Processing block - States how the BEL framework should process this equivalence document NamespaceReference block - States which namespace this equivalence document maps
EquivalenceHeaderProcessor  
NamespaceReferenceBlock CitationBlock encapsulates the '[NamespaceReference]' block of a BEL equivalence document.
